query_text: SELECT STDDEV("catalog_returns"."cr_order_number"), VARIANCE("catalog_returns"."cr_ship_mode_sk"), SUM("catalog_returns"."cr_refunded_cash"), AVG("catalog_returns"."cr_return_ship_cost") FROM "web_site" CROSS JOIN "income_band" CROSS JOIN "reason" CROSS JOIN "ship_mode" CROSS JOIN "catalog_returns" WHERE "reason"."r_reason_id" LIKE '%u%' AND "income_band"."ib_income_band_sk" < 2 ORDER BY COUNT(*) ASC;
SELECT MAX("date_dim"."d_dow"), AVG("date_dim"."d_year"), MAX("date_dim"."d_fy_year") FROM "date_dim" CROSS JOIN "time_dim";

SELECT MAX("web_site"."web_close_date_sk"), VARIANCE("web_page"."wp_access_date_sk"), COUNT(*) FROM "dbgen_version" CROSS JOIN "web_page" CROSS JOIN "web_site" WHERE "dbgen_version"."dv_version" LIKE '%e%' AND "dbgen_version"."dv_version" IS NOT NULL AND "web_site"."web_city" != 'Fairview' AND "web_page"."wp_type" != 'protected                                         ' AND "web_page"."wp_link_count" > 25 ORDER BY COUNT(*) DESC;

SELECT AVG("item"."i_manager_id"), AVG("customer"."c_first_sales_date_sk"), MIN("item"."i_item_sk") FROM "customer" CROSS JOIN "item" WHERE "item"."i_class" = 'tables                                            ' AND "item"."i_class" IS NOT NULL AND "item"."i_manufact" LIKE '%a%' GROUP BY "item"."i_container", "customer"."c_last_name", "item"."i_class";

SELECT SUM("customer_address"."ca_address_sk"), MAX("store_returns"."sr_addr_sk") FROM "store" CROSS JOIN "customer_demographics" CROSS JOIN "customer_address" CROSS JOIN "store_returns" CROSS JOIN "household_demographics" WHERE "household_demographics"."hd_dep_count" > 3 AND "store"."s_street_name" LIKE '%u%' AND "customer_demographics"."cd_dep_employed_count" = 6 AND "store"."s_number_employees" >= 262 AND "customer_demographics"."cd_gender" LIKE '%a%';
SELECT COUNT(*), MIN("catalog_page"."cp_start_date_sk"), SUM("catalog_page"."cp_catalog_number"), STDDEV("catalog_page"."cp_end_date_sk") FROM "catalog_page";

SELECT MAX("web_returns"."wr_return_ship_cost"), VARIANCE("web_returns"."wr_reversed_charge"), AVG("web_returns"."wr_net_loss"), MAX("web_returns"."wr_returned_date_sk"), MAX("web_returns"."wr_returning_addr_sk") FROM "web_returns" WHERE "web_returns"."wr_return_ship_cost" < 3308.8288790287957 AND "web_returns"."wr_returning_addr_sk" > 2;

SELECT VARIANCE("income_band"."ib_upper_bound"), COUNT(*), VARIANCE("household_demographics"."hd_dep_count"), MIN("household_demographics"."hd_vehicle_count") FROM "household_demographics" CROSS JOIN "income_band" WHERE "income_band"."ib_lower_bound" <= 0 AND "household_demographics"."hd_buy_potential" LIKE '%u%' AND "household_demographics"."hd_buy_potential" IS NULL GROUP BY "household_demographics"."hd_buy_potential", "household_demographics"."hd_buy_potential" LIMIT 10;

SELECT COUNT(*), STDDEV("web_returns"."wr_return_quantity"), MAX("web_returns"."wr_returned_time_sk"), MIN("customer_demographics"."cd_dep_employed_count") FROM "customer_demographics" CROSS JOIN "web_returns" WHERE "web_returns"."wr_reversed_charge" > 0.0 AND "web_returns"."wr_reversed_charge" IS NOT NULL AND "web_returns"."wr_web_page_sk" < 57 AND "customer_demographics"."cd_credit_rating" != 'Unknown   ' AND "customer_demographics"."cd_dep_count" > 4 AND "customer_demographics"."cd_demo_sk" >= 1920800 AND "customer_demographics"."cd_demo_sk" IS NOT NULL ORDER BY COUNT(*) ASC LIMIT 100;

SELECT COUNT(*), SUM("web_sales"."ws_bill_customer_sk"), AVG("web_sales"."ws_ext_tax") FROM "income_band" CROSS JOIN "web_sales" WHERE "web_sales"."ws_ship_date_sk" > 2452762 AND "web_sales"."ws_sales_price" <= 202.04701349976978 AND "web_sales"."ws_sales_price" IS NOT NULL AND "income_band"."ib_lower_bound" <= 183303 AND "web_sales"."ws_ship_mode_sk" > 13 ORDER BY COUNT(*) DESC;

SELECT MAX("catalog_sales"."cs_call_center_sk"), VARIANCE("catalog_sales"."cs_net_paid") FROM "web_returns" CROSS JOIN "catalog_sales" CROSS JOIN "web_page" WHERE "catalog_sales"."cs_net_paid_inc_ship_tax" >= 35067.14207918736 AND "web_returns"."wr_return_amt_inc_tax" = 18301.795847183013 AND "catalog_sales"."cs_net_paid" > 0.0 AND "catalog_sales"."cs_ship_addr_sk" >= 1 AND "web_returns"."wr_return_amt" > 10926.034154978759 LIMIT 10;
SELECT MAX("item"."i_brand_id") FROM "item" WHERE "item"."i_item_sk" = 14689 OR "item"."i_item_sk" IS NULL GROUP BY "item"."i_size", "item"."i_manufact", "item"."i_formulation" ORDER BY COUNT(*) ASC;

SELECT VARIANCE("item"."i_brand_id"), STDDEV("item"."i_wholesale_cost"), SUM("item"."i_wholesale_cost"), MIN("item"."i_wholesale_cost"), COUNT(*) FROM "item" WHERE "item"."i_brand" != 'corpunivamalg #5                                  ' AND "item"."i_item_sk" < 18000 AND "item"."i_color" = 'goldenrod           ' AND "item"."i_units" LIKE '%a%' AND "item"."i_brand" != 'edu packmaxi #10                                  ' GROUP BY "item"."i_brand", "item"."i_item_id", "item"."i_item_id" HAVING AVG(1) < 85 ORDER BY COUNT(*) DESC;
SELECT COUNT(*) FROM "ship_mode" WHERE "ship_mode"."sm_contract" = '5FKNB0j8aaqTB       ' OR "ship_mode"."sm_ship_mode_sk" = 11 ORDER BY COUNT(*) DESC;

SELECT MAX("ship_mode"."sm_ship_mode_sk"), COUNT(*), MIN("ship_mode"."sm_ship_mode_sk"), MAX("ship_mode"."sm_ship_mode_sk") FROM "ship_mode" WHERE "ship_mode"."sm_ship_mode_id" LIKE '%o%' AND "ship_mode"."sm_ship_mode_sk" != 5 GROUP BY "ship_mode"."sm_ship_mode_sk", "ship_mode"."sm_ship_mode_sk" ORDER BY "ship_mode"."sm_ship_mode_sk", "ship_mode"."sm_ship_mode_sk" DESC LIMIT 1000;

SELECT MIN("store_returns"."sr_returned_date_sk"), MAX("store_sales"."ss_net_profit"), MAX("store_returns"."sr_customer_sk") FROM "store_returns" CROSS JOIN "store_sales" WHERE "store_returns"."sr_refunded_cash" >= 14887.06 AND "store_returns"."sr_refunded_cash" IS NULL AND "store_sales"."ss_item_sk" != 7404 AND "store_returns"."sr_returned_date_sk" = 2451000;
SELECT "time_dim"."t_shift" FROM "time_dim" WHERE "time_dim"."t_time_id" = 'AAAAAAAAHPDLAAAA' ORDER BY "time_dim"."t_meal_time" ASC LIMIT 10;
SELECT "web_site"."web_company_id", "web_site"."web_street_type" FROM "web_site" ORDER BY "web_site"."web_manager" ASC LIMIT 100;
SELECT "store_sales"."ss_ext_list_price" FROM "store_sales" WHERE "store_sales"."ss_promo_sk" = 185 AND "store_sales"."ss_list_price" < 1.0 ORDER BY "store_sales"."ss_wholesale_cost" ASC LIMIT 1;
SELECT "catalog_returns"."cr_catalog_page_sk", "catalog_returns"."cr_warehouse_sk" FROM "catalog_returns" WHERE "catalog_returns"."cr_item_sk" = 2708 LIMIT 1;
SELECT "catalog_sales"."cs_promo_sk" FROM "catalog_sales" WHERE "catalog_sales"."cs_item_sk" = 1 LIMIT 100;
SELECT "reason"."r_reason_sk", "reason"."r_reason_desc" FROM "reason" WHERE "reason"."r_reason_sk" = 1 AND "reason"."r_reason_sk" >= 35 LIMIT 1;
SELECT "web_returns"."wr_returned_date_sk", "web_returns"."wr_web_page_sk", "web_returns"."wr_reversed_charge" FROM "web_returns" WHERE "web_returns"."wr_item_sk" = 11156 LIMIT 100;
SELECT "date_dim"."d_last_dom" FROM "date_dim" WHERE "date_dim"."d_date_sk" = 2488070 LIMIT 100;
SELECT "web_site"."web_zip", "web_site"."web_name", "web_site"."web_company_name" FROM "web_site" WHERE "web_site"."web_site_sk" = 15 AND "web_site"."web_open_date_sk" < 2450579 LIMIT 10;
SELECT "income_band"."ib_upper_bound" FROM "income_band" ORDER BY "income_band"."ib_lower_bound" ASC LIMIT 10;
SELECT "reason"."r_reason_id", "reason"."r_reason_sk" FROM "reason" WHERE "reason"."r_reason_sk" = 12 LIMIT 10;
SELECT "catalog_page"."cp_end_date_sk", "catalog_page"."cp_start_date_sk" FROM "catalog_page" WHERE "catalog_page"."cp_catalog_page_sk" = 8121 LIMIT 100;
SELECT "customer_demographics"."cd_education_status" FROM "customer_demographics" WHERE "customer_demographics"."cd_demo_sk" = 493306 LIMIT 10;
SELECT "promotion"."p_discount_active" FROM "promotion" WHERE "promotion"."p_promo_sk" = 300 ORDER BY "promotion"."p_end_date_sk" ASC LIMIT 1;
SELECT "web_site"."web_zip", "web_site"."web_site_id" FROM "web_site" WHERE "web_site"."web_site_sk" = 24 LIMIT 100;
SELECT "store"."s_city", "store"."s_country" FROM "store" LIMIT 1;
SELECT "date_dim"."d_current_week" FROM "date_dim" WHERE "date_dim"."d_date_sk" = 2415022 LIMIT 1;
SELECT "time_dim"."t_time_sk" FROM "time_dim" WHERE "time_dim"."t_minute" = 59 LIMIT 10;
SELECT "dbgen_version"."dv_version" FROM "dbgen_version" LIMIT 1;
SELECT "customer_demographics"."cd_marital_status", "customer_demographics"."cd_credit_rating" FROM "customer_demographics" WHERE "customer_demographics"."cd_demo_sk" = 89665 LIMIT 1;

SELECT "call_center"."cc_division", "call_center"."cc_mkt_class", "call_center"."cc_class" FROM "call_center" WHERE "call_center"."cc_call_center_sk" = 1 ORDER BY "call_center"."cc_county" ASC LIMIT 10;
SELECT "catalog_sales"."cs_sales_price" FROM "catalog_sales" WHERE "catalog_sales"."cs_item_sk" = 18000 LIMIT 1;
